My client Anne was sooo excited to sit in my chair! Her words to me as she sat down was "Sarah thank you for answering your calling” 🥹🥹. She just kept expressing to me over and over how fond she is of my craft. I get clients like this once in a while and it will always be the single most humbling, most encouraging and heartfelt moments I ever get to experience in the course of my career. The best part is they always seem to be TIMELY! 

I’m sharing this moment with y’all to say this, GOD IS SO GOOD! He knows just what to do and when to do it. He knows just what you need! Y’all have no idea how many times I have contemplated and even made up my mind to QUIT makeup artistry! Everyone glorifies this entrepreneur lifestyle but let me tell you it’s not for the faint of heart! 

No one broadcasts the obstacles, and losses they face because let’s be honest it just does not feel good! It’s on going challenges, on going stress, on going trials and errors, on going judgments and speculations and sometimes that’s just more than one feel like they can take or handle! But God will do it every time! He will send that affirmation, that reassurance! 

To the few that still engages with my content, the few that still book services, the few that refers my services, the few that supports me in ways I may not even know or notice, front the bottom of my heart THANK YOU🥹🙏🏾🙌🏾!
